{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_21025.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303801,"motion":1,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304001,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"narrationBg":"bg_adv_21025.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"<Historical Research Club - Provisional Room>","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story13","chara":[{"id":303801}],"nameLeft":"Mikura","nameRight":"Temari","narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"...Yeah. Sorry, Amane."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303801}],"textLeft":"You guys be careful out there, too.@Hope you stay safe."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303801}],"nameNarration":"","narration":"*Beep.*","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21025.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"id":303801,"motion":101}],"narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"I told her about how Mihono got away from us..."},{"chara":[{"id":303801}],"textLeft":"Amane said she'd pass it along to everyone else, too."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304001,"motion":100}],"textRight":"I let my guard down. I didn't expect her to be waiting@to ambush us..."},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"textRight":"I should've tried harder to take Ruri's feelings into@consideration."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303801}],"textLeft":"What do you mean?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304001,"motion":300}],"textRight":"You remember what happened on the last day of@filming, right?"},{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":1,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/3003_act_picture.ExportJson","zOrder":"charaFront"}],"autoTurnLast":1.2,"bg":"bg_adv_21532.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303802,"motion":300,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303902,"motion":0,"pos":2,"tear":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"sepiaFrame"},{"chara":[{"id":303802}],"nameLeft":"Tsukihiko","nameRight":"Ruri","textLeft":"...I've loved you ever since I laid eyes on you.@...The whole time since...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303802,"motion":101},{"eyeClose":1,"id":303902,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"...I was going to break things off with her...@for good..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303802},{"eyeClose":0,"id":303902}],"textLeft":"And swear to live...@my whole life... for you..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303902,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"tear":1}],"textRight":"...?!"},{"autoTurnLast":1.2,"bg":"bg_adv_21025.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303801,"motion":1,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304001,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"deleteArmatureList":[1],"narrationBg":"bg_adv_21025.jpg","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"nameRight":"Temari","textRight":"Because we kept the \"real\" script hidden from@Mihono until then...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"textRight":"...that was the first time Ruri ever learned@the truth."},{"chara":[{"id":303801,"motion":101}],"textLeft":"...You're right."},{"chara":[{"id":304001,"motion":300}],"textRight":"But she didn't have any proof to back up what@you said."},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"textRight":"So right now, what \"she\" wants to know most of all..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303801,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"Is whether the \"Tsukihiko\" I performed as was@telling the truth or not."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304001,"motion":100}],"textRight":"Right."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304001}],"textRight":"And shortly thereafter, \"she\" found out about@the diary."},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"bg":"bg_adv_21531.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304001,"motion":200,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303902,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304001,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Temari","textLeft":"She found Tsukihiko's own diary, written in the days@leading up to his period of amnesia.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":303902,"lipSynch":0,"motion":400}],"nameRight":"Seira","textRight":"...?!"},{"autoTurnLast":1.2,"bg":"bg_adv_21025.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303801,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304001,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"narrationBg":"bg_adv_21025.jpg","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":303801,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Mikura","textLeft":"...Hence why she was lying in wait to steal the diary@from us.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"nameRight":"Temari","textRight":"Indeed."},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"textRight":"That's just how badly she needed to know."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303801,"lipSynch":0,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"id":304001,"motion":100}],"textRight":"Ruri is probably reading the last pages as we speak..."},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"textRight":"...and finding out that his words were true."},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"textRight":"That Tsukihiko did love her with all his heart..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304001,"motion":400}],"textRight":"And that despite that, she took his life with her own@two hands."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303801,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"So what's Ruri going to do next, having found that@out?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"textRight":"...[chara:304001:lipSynch_0][wait:1.2][chara:304001:lipSynch_1]I have no idea."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304001,"motion":200}],"textRight":"By the time Ruri committed her murder-suicide@with Tsukihiko..."},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"textRight":"...she had long since lost her senses."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304001}],"textRight":"And right after that, we thrust an even crueler truth@upon her."},{"chara":[{"id":304001,"motion":300}],"textRight":"Whatever scrap of her heart may have been left@unharmed at that point..."},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"textRight":"I'm sure it's been reduced to dust by now."},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"textRight":"So I can hardly predict what actions she might take@next."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303801,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"...@..."},{"chara":[{"id":304001,"motion":200}],"textRight":"To think that wishing for a miracle would bring@about such a tragic result..."},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"textRight":"What a horrible ending."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303801,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"Huh? A miracle...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":304001,"motion":0,"mouthOpen":1}],"textRight":"Ah...!"},{"chara":[{"id":304001,"mouthOpen":0}],"textRight":"Sorry. We've been rushing around all morning, so I@forgot to tell you."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304001,"motion":400}],"textRight":"Sheâ€” that is to say, Ruri..."},{"chara":[{"id":304001}],"textRight":"...was a Magical Girl."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}